    "body": "Thinking about it a bit more, I think you're right, since the `WINDOW_UPDATE` following unacknowledged `SETTINGS_INITIAL_WINDOW_SIZE` could put the total over the limit after `SETTINGS_INITIAL_WINDOW_SIZE` gets updated on the receiving side.\r\n\r\nNevertheless, this could lead to a weird deadlock or pause, but the particular case that I'm worried about will be fixed by https://github.com/grpc/grpc/issues/13062 anyway.\r\n\r\nThanks!"
